# No Cursor branding

Never add "Made with Cursor", "Built with Cursor", or similar Cursor attribution anywhere:

- Pull request titles and descriptions
- README, comments, commit messages
- UI footers, HTML meta tags, or generated docs
- Any user-facing or repository-facing text

Do not link to cursor.com as a credit line. This project should not advertise the editor.
